overview.en: HEMP(tenjove) is a cannabis company founded by NASDAQ listed company Shanggao(NASDAQ: TYHT), dedicated to the production of high quality Cannabidiol(CBD) based on the blockchain-passenger economy model.
overview.zh: HEMP(新麻生物)是由纳斯达克上市公司尚高（NASDAQ: TYHT）发起成立，基于区块链电子凭证经济模式下，致力于种植、加工、生产高品质大麻二酚(CBD)及衍生品的公司。
